translations: 表现派作家；表现主义艺术家

sentences.sentence: She helped me get boned up on my modern expressionist art.
sentences.translation: 她帮我强化突击了现代表现主义艺术。

sentences.sentence: Expressionist graphics, decisive slogans and modernist wit pervade these images.
sentences.translation: 表象派作家生动的，坚定的标语和现代主义作者遍及街头的风趣画作。

sentences.sentence: I am learning so much from her.She helped me get boned up on my modern expressionist art.
